{"tid":2267916,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"共產黨：7人暴動案錯判正全方位向律政司施壓盡快上訴","createTime":"2020-11-02T11:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-02T12:06:12.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6969bd47f48644bd021e5bd9edc9d37f3deee3ef","tid":2267916,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:52:34.000Z","msg":"周浩鼎質疑法官處理8.31暴動案交替控罪時出錯<br />\n<br />\n7名男女被控去年8月31日在灣仔暴動，區域法院上周六裁定7人全部罪名不成立。民建聯立法會議員周浩鼎認為，法庭在交替控罪可能出現錯誤，希望律政司盡快研究提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n周浩鼎指，判詞顯示，法庭至少在交替控罪的處理上可能出現錯誤，律政司原本預備以非法集結罪作交替控罪，但法庭一口拒絕處理，他認為在此法律原則可能出現錯誤。他說，很多公眾都反映對判決感到失望，擔心判決會令人誤以為參與暴動，不需要負上法律代價，變相鼓勵違法行動。<br />\n<br />\n律政司日前回覆查詢時說，就今次案件，正研究法官的判決理據和主控官的報告，然後決定是否需要跟進。至於同案的社工陳虹秀，早前已因為表面證據不成立，被撤銷暴動控罪。律政司指，已經根據《區域法院條例》第84條，以案件呈述的方式提出上訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557960-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557960-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=Vpe8FAkBT2vLq%2FWrgjLHxRT9vY2lxR77dvs0GIZdErU%3D&h=5174cf32\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1557960-20201102.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=6285fe19\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1557960-20201102.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"faf3dc4af5b737cbda35d51926035b2ccabc69a0","tid":2267916,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:54:14.000Z","msg":"呀鼎 你好似連bar都唔係wor <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/how.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70217c329c54caea2dbc2e89a3db91ef69d8d9bb","tid":2267916,"uid":65743,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-02T11:54:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gqEiqmd.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgqEiqmd.gif&h=d141fb31&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e368ccbc135931db7f3465ed1b6ec46deddf347","tid":2267916,"uid":16